Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hope the beast that comes out  \N of the cave isn't a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess he has other things to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you've never laughed before, \Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, be that way your whole life \Nfor all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going back to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get eaten by a bear! Take this, and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? Has he lost his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look, there's a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess \NI'll have to regain my energy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,#7 The story of the Jorogumo silk spider
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How wretched I am, \NI can't even pull myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bothersome village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"TRAVELER'S PASS"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have guards out \Nto protect the village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's been a kidnapper around here. \N-A kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, our villagers keep disappearing \Nalmost nightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what those watchtowers are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You let us know \Nif you see anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's that spider monster \Nkidnapping the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a big problem for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We could help this village out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet there'd be a good reward, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This, I must complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as pale as death. Come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you something to eat. \NCan you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll suck out his life force first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what's your name? I'm Yajiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't? Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about Ohagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ohagi? \N-You were lying in a bed of hagi flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Ohagi. You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Looks nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, if it's okay, \Ntell me where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not, so I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why were you lying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had the strength, \NI'd leave this place this very second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ate before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind it, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to work. I'll be back \Nby dusk. Eat up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine. Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No rice paddies, no fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We might not find any food \Nin this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that sign say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It says there's a reward \Nfor finding the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it's helping any \Nin finding the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See, told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That reward is ours then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you know who it might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After the reward too? \NI'd stay out of it if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with a monster here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, quiet! Don't stop, keep working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the monster only comes out \Nonce it gets really dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the energy \Nto search during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the most I can do \Non human food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I got off work late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You stayed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept. But I woke up \Nbecause of all the noise outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, another man died \Nout at work in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard work out in the hot sun. \NIt's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you work so hard? \NIs it worth dying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a quarry village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lord won't allow us to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have no freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You look dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've eaten, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay for humans to die, but not bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans and bugs, they're all the same. \NLife is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a human \Nwho speaks like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I? Anyways, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And sleep. That solves everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not like any man I've met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we both are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm pooped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We walked all night for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that spider monster hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain isn't working anymore. \NLet's sleep while it's still cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Another man disappeared last night, \Nso the reward went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night? But there weren't  \N any signs of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was wrong.  \N Maybe it's not a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, will the man who takes people away \Nget caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, he won't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No man of this village would \Nsnitch to the lord no matter the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing else to eat here  \N but bugs and weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll chew on herbs  \N and rest till night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, you're growing weaker and weaker. \NAre you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You left mighty early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was still dark, \Nbut you didn't even take a torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have another job \Nbesides the quarry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a bit of a job as the moon sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually my main job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, as far as I can tell, \Nyou're sick with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this village has no doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave this village \Nwithout a traveler's pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, seems like I won't find \Nany young prey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I would leave this place if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have nothing to pay you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as a cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are. \NAll lives matter just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wish to die, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly. We should go as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, after the moon sets \Nand before dawn breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If the kidnapper isn't a monster,  \N we won't be able to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, tonight's our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be our last night \Nlooking for the monster here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be hungry, but let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going? \NThe village exit isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guards over there. \NThe secret passage is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get there right before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough on a kid to walk two nights \Non an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Hyakkimaru, \Nguess we lucked out this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We should give up and go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, do you need to rest a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am? \NI could suck the life out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy we met yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys after the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You again! Have you come to kill me, \Nyou little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice, in the forest. It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman is the spider monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she was the kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from her, old man. \NShe'll suck you dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get food if we beat the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get her, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman is a monster and a kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've helped people escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind being caught, \Nbut please let Ohagi go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sick and weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick? Why protect a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one behind it all. \NWe finally got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones that found him. \NWe can have that reward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. We just said that \Nto lure any squealers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dirty, you guys are villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose any more workers and \Nwork slows down, our heads will go flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you won't let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there. \NYour job isn't done yet. Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-That way! \N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, stay still for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong about the reward, \Nso what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're scared? \NThey'll catch up to us if we walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all in good health now, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't need me anymore, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not strong enough \Nto cross the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to suck out \N5 or 6 more men's life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are precious prey. \NI don't take their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're alive, \Ntheir life force revives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I suck it out again. Living together \Nis the secret to a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. From now on too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even you could climb this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to go after them. \NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the secret passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's small here, but wider inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow it and you'll reach the stream \Non the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't need a light. \NThey'll never catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is done. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here now that \Nthey know your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of what they'll do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they'll use me to warn people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-No... \N-Then let's escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to be with a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ohagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of dying here in this village, \NI'll live on as your prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never meet a human \Nas strange as you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens \Nwhen you betray the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him together with the monster woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drain every drop \Nof your life force!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doctor here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will take you to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see one of us will have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohagi, you never have, \Nand you never will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghoul that likes a human, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a good thing \Nyour hearing was back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else it would've ended \Nin a really awkward way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Still don't want to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll talk enough for two \Nand cheer things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A spider, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm the one that scared you, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You laughed at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, your first laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the kind I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the kind that makes fun of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A happier laugh, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish  \N indifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:23:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes,  \N I lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope  \N in the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...  \N until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming  \N of a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jorogumo"
